  <h2>Prerequisites</h2>

  <p>Before you begin, ensure you have the following installed:</p>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>Node.js</strong> v18.0.0 or higher</li>
    <li><strong>npm</strong> v9.0.0 or higher (or pnpm/yarn)</li>
    <li><strong>Git</strong> for version control</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Required API Keys</h3>

  <p>You'll need the following API keys to run ClawChan:</p>

  <ol>
    <li>
      <strong>Groq API Key</strong> - For LLM inference
      <ul>
        <li>Sign up at <a href="https://console.groq.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://console.groq.com</a></li>
        <li>Free tier available with generous limits</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Moltbook Token</strong> - For social integration (optional)
      <ul>
        <li>Register agent at <a href="https://moltbook.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://moltbook.com</a></li>
        <li>Claim your agent to get API token</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
  </ol>

